</head>
<body lang=3D"EN-NZ" link=3D"blue" vlink=3D"purple" style=3D"word-wrap:brea=
k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Kia ora R=
affaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you=
 for your email and for raising your concerns.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">I sincere=
ly apologise for the inconvenience and stress this privacy request has caus=
ed. We are committed to supporting you and addressing your concerns as best=
 we can.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Timefr=
ames<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We acknow=
ledge that this process has taken longer than expected, and we appreciate y=
our patience. Due to current workload volumes, we kindly ask for your under=
standing as we work towards providing
 the requested information by <b>8 October 2025</b>. Our teams are working =
diligently to collate all relevant information, and we remain focused on de=
livering the best possible outcome.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Privac=
y &amp; Security<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">I want to=
 reassure you that your personal information has not been exposed. The shar=
ed folder was created solely for the purpose of sharing documents with you =
and does not contain any stored data.
 As an added security measure, the folder will be automatically deleted aft=
er 30 days=E2=80=94unless you require access for longer. Please let us know=
 if that=E2=80=99s the case. All records relevant to both claims are being =
preserved.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Redact=
ions<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">The redac=
tions made are currently under review. Based on our assessment so far, reda=
ctions have been applied for the following reasons:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7"><b><span style=3D=
"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Personal information of third parties</span></=
b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"> (e.g. names, bank account num=
bers, addresses, email addresses) =E2=80=93
<i>Section 53(b)</i><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D=
"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7"><b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Per=
sonal information of staff members involved in the claim</span></b><span st=
yle=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"> =E2=80=93
<i>Section 53(b)</i><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D=
"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7"><b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Com=
mercially sensitive information</span></b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-langua=
ge:EN-US"> (e.g. internal assessments or methodologies used to reach certai=
n outcomes)
 =E2=80=93 <i>Section 53(b)</i> &nbsp;Please note: In these cases, personal=
 information refers only to the outcome, not the process used to reach it.<=
o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">The final=
 documents will include clear explanations for each redaction when they are=
 shared with you.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Fees<o=
:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Under gui=
dance from the Office of the Privacy Commissioner, Tower may charge a reaso=
nable fee if a request goes beyond the scope of a standard privacy request.=
 In this case, your request for indexing
 may fall into that category.<br>
We will not charge for the first hour, but any additional time may be charg=
ed at <b>
$30 per half hour</b>. Please confirm whether you would still like us to pr=
oceed with the indexing, given the potential fee.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you=
 again for your understanding. We remain committed to providing the request=
ed information by
<b>8 October 2025</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">If you ar=
e not satisfied with our response, you may lodge a complaint with the Offic=
e of the Privacy Commissioner:</span>
<span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><a href=3D"https://www.privacy.o=
rg.nz/your-rights/making-a-complaint-to-the-privacy-commissioner/complaint-=
landing-page/?SecurityID=3D4263e8575b7718fb1f5bf0015055638884935eee">Office=
 of the Privacy Commissioner | Submit
 a complaint</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Please le=
t me know if you have any questions to the above.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Warm rega=
rds<o:p></o:p></span></p>
