Classification: Sensitive<br>
</p>
<div style=3D"border:none;border-top:solid #E1E1E1 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0cm =
0cm 0cm">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;fo=
nt-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">From:</span></b><span lang=3D"EN-=
US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"> =
Raffaella del Prete &lt;raffaellanz@icloud.com&gt;
<br>
<b>Sent:</b> Sunday, 28 September 2025 4:44 pm<br>
<b>To:</b> Privacy &lt;Privacy@tower.co.nz&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Privacy Request<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora team, Thank you for your email. I=E2=80=
=99d like to clarify a few points so we can bring this to a timely conclusi=
on: Timeframes My Privacy Act request was made
 on 1 July 2025. The statutory timeframe has passed. On 15 September 2025 I=
 was told<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora team,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your email.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I=E2=80=99d like to clarify a few points so we can b=
ring this to a timely conclusion:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Timeframes</b><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">My Privacy Act request was made on 1 July 2025. The =
statutory timeframe has passed. On 15 September 2025 I was told the additio=
nal material would be provided within 5 working days. Could you please expl=
ain why the date has now moved to
 8 October, and on what basis?<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Privacy &amp; security</b><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">There have been several issues to date (broken Share=
File links, visibility of another customer=E2=80=99s folder, and access not=
 tied to my identity). I appreciate that you have notified OPC and recreate=
d folders; however, these incidents, combined
 with delay, have caused avoidable stress. Please confirm the containment s=
teps taken and that all records relevant to both claims are being preserved=
.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Redactions</b><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">The material provided so far is heavily redacted wit=
hout identification of the grounds relied upon. For every redaction or with=
holding, please set out the specific ground and provide the least-redacted =
version possible.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Fees</b><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I do not accept that a fee is appropriate in this ca=
se. No charges were mentioned previously, and it is Tower=E2=80=99s respons=
ibility to maintain and retrieve my claim information. If you now believe a=
 fee is required, please set out:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1">
the legal basis you rely on,<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=
=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l1 level1 l=
fo1">
the specific activities the fee would cover, and<o:p></o:p></li><li class=
=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;=
mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1">
the total amount, and how this is &nbsp;calculated and why you believe it i=
s &nbsp;reasonable<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Delivery</b><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please confirm that the complete files for both clai=
ms=E2=80=94together with an index and the specific grounds for any redactio=
ns=E2=80=94will be provided by 8 October 2025, without further extension an=
d without charge.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">I remain keen to resolve this directly. If it cannot=
 be resolved on this basis, I will consider referring the matter to the Off=
ice of the Privacy Commissioner<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Raffaella del Prete<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">On 26 Sep 2025, at 8:13<span style=3D"font-family:&q=
uot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>AM, Privacy &lt;<a href=3D"mail=
to:Privacy@tower.co.nz">Privacy@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Dear Rafaella,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your email.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">As Megan mentioned in her response on 15 September 2=
025, the additional information you requested will be provided by<span clas=
s=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b>8 October 2025</b>.<o:p></o:p><=
/p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Regarding the fees: we can only provide an estimate =
if you agree for us to proceed with the additional work, which includes ind=
exing by date, author, short description, and system/location.<o:p></o:p></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We will also review the redactions made and assess w=
hat can be done to meet your request.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Warm regards<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
