mily:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-U=
S" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Ra=
ffaella
 del Prete &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:raffaellanz@icloud.com">raffaellanz@icloud=
.com</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Sent:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Thursday, 25=
 September 2025 5:45 pm<br>
<b>To:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Privacy &lt;<a=
 href=3D"mailto:Privacy@tower.co.nz">Privacy@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Cc:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Megan Jensen &=
lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz">Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz</a>=
&gt;; Lance O'Riley &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Lance.ORiley@tower.co.nz">Lance.O=
Riley@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Re: Priva=
cy Request<br>
<b>Importance:</b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>High</=
span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora,=
 Thank you for your response and for the documents provided. Having reviewe=
d the material so far, it still appears incomplete and not up to date. Coul=
d you please: 1) ETA for full disclosure
 Provide an ETA for when the full file will</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your response and for the documents pr=
ovided. Having reviewed the material so far, it still appears incomplete an=
d not up to date. Could you please:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">1) ETA for full disclosure<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Provide an ETA for when the full file will be shared=
, including all material identified in your =E2=80=9Centerprise-wide search=
.=E2=80=9D If rolling disclosure is being used, please confirm what further=
 releases I should expect and by when.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">2) Fees<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please confirm that no fees will be charged for this=
 request. Given this request arises from Tower=E2=80=99s own system handlin=
g and relates to my personal information, I consider fees inappropriate. &n=
bsp;If Tower still intends to impose fees, please
 provide a written bill/estimate in advance detailing the calculation (time=
, hourly rate, and scope of work).<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">By way of reassurance, I am a professional in IT and=
 experienced with insurance systems. I would be happy to review the search =
approach to ensure the search is both appropriate and efficient, and to avo=
id unnecessary duplication or administrative
 burden.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">3) Redactions<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Redactions to date appear to extend beyond simple re=
moval of other people=E2=80=99s names and personal identifiers. Please conf=
irm the specific legal grounds relied upon for each redaction or withholdin=
g, and explain why partial release was not
 reasonably practicable. Where =E2=80=9Ccommercial sensitivity=E2=80=9D is =
claimed, I ask that non-sensitive technical content and valuation inputs (s=
cope descriptions, quantities, allowances, rates, contingencies) still be d=
isclosed, as these are required for transparency
 and fairness in assessing my claim.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Raffaella<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><br>
<br>
<br>
<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">On 25 Sep 2025, at 1:01<span style=3D"font-family:&q=
uot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>PM, Privacy &lt;<a href=3D"mail=
to:Privacy@tower.co.nz">Privacy@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Kia ora Rafaella,<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you for your detailed email and for raising th=
ese concerns. I want to acknowledge the stress and frustration this situati=
on has caused, especially given the circumstances you're already navigating=
 following the fire. We take your
 concerns seriously and are committed to addressing them thoroughly and res=
pectfully.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">A) Security / Containment<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We sincerely apologise for the oversight regarding t=
he link access. We have now:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0cm" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2">Disabled the curr=
ent ShareFile link.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-lis=
t:l6 level1 lfo2">Initiated a reissue of access that is restricted and tied=
 solely to your email address.<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;<=
/span><a href=3D"https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/towernz.sharefile.com/d=
-sb3797728cdc745088741e36a60cdfbe1__;!!NPvfczxIteVBjg!AVYtEjQ8mHMqoFnPEKGMV=
depnpgqPwlpGXqwGdB_c__-ag19JJWSVWsliQ2qKr_bYN42jSjTXsE9PSFk-IrVVCVN$">https=
://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sb3797728cdc745088741e36a60cdfbe1
 [towernz.sharefile.com]</a><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=
=3D"mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2">A full audit log from ShareFile, including act=
ivity, and access events. This has been uploaded to your file.<o:p></o:p></=
li></ul>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We have used the Privacy Commissioners =E2=80=9CNoti=
fyUs=E2=80=9D tool as requested on 15 September to review whether this inci=
dent meets the threshold for a notifiable privacy breach under the Privacy =
Act. We confirm the outcome of that assessment return
 being unlikely event, due to that Tower can see who has access to the link=
 and the link has only been shared to yourself. The report is also included=
 in your file in the link.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">B) Substantive Privacy Act Response<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We acknowledge your original request and the legal e=
ntitlements under IPP6 of the Privacy Act 2020. We are now conducting a fre=
sh, enterprise-wide search across all relevant systems and third-party prov=
iders to ensure completeness. This
 includes:<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0cm" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3">Internal communic=
ations (email, IM, call logs, transcripts)<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoN=
ormal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3">Third-party instructions and corre=
spondence<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level=
1 lfo3">Site media and technical reports<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNor=
mal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3">ShareFile configuration and access l=
ogs. Already included.<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">However, we won=E2=80=99t be providing a document in=
dex for this privacy request, as creating one would be a significant admini=
strative task and isn=E2=80=99t something we=E2=80=99re required to do unde=
r the Privacy Act. The Act requires us to provide access to
 existing personal information, but not to create new documents or indexes.=
 We=E2=80=99d also like to note that if a request is particularly detailed =
or requires a lot of extra work to process, we are entitled to charge a rea=
sonable fee to cover the administrative
 costs involved.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Grounds for any redactions or withholdings, however,=
 some documents have been withheld or redacted because they contain the per=
sonal information of other individuals, which we are legally required to pr=
otect under the Privacy Act. Additionally,
 certain documents include commercially sensitive information=E2=80=94such =
as contractor pricing or internal business processes, that cannot be disclo=
sed. We understand this may be disappointing, and we=E2=80=99re committed t=
o being as transparent as possible within those
 legal and commercial boundaries. This said, we will provide more detail wh=
ere we can on the specific redactions.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">C) Records Preservation<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We confirm that all records relating to your claims =
are being preserved until both matters are fully resolved and all requested=
 documentation has been provided.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We appreciate your patience and your clear articulat=
ion of the issues. Please know that we are treating this with urgency and c=
are, and we are committed to resolving it directly with you.<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Warm regards<o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
</div>
