yle=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5">Internal communications: emails and IM (e.g=
., Teams/Slack).<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l=
3 level1 lfo5">Call recordings/transcripts for all calls with me (inbound/o=
utbound), any video calls, and voicemail.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNo=
rmal" style=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5">SMS/texts and chat messages with me=
.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5">=
Instructions to/from assessors and contractors, all quotes/scopes/variation=
s, and native costing files/spreadsheets used to build any scope/SOW.<o:p><=
/o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5">Site me=
dia: all photos and videos.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D=
"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5">Testing/technical reports: moisture logs; soot/sm=
oke/odour assessments; HVAC/duct contamination; asbestos sampling/clearance=
s; electrical, gas, and engineering reports/results.<o:p></o:p></li><li cla=
ss=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5">Third-party corresponden=
ce relating to my claims.<o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"m=
so-list:l3 level1 lfo5">ShareFile configuration and access/audit logs for l=
inks used to provide my data.<o:p></o:p></li></ul>
